1
00:00:03,340 --> 00:00:09,180
♪You're the unattainable star♪

2
00:00:09,300 --> 00:00:14,940
♪I'm the tiniest dust in the world♪

3
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,820
♪With all the sincerity I can muster♪

4
00:00:18,020 --> 00:00:20,860
♪For your kiss after the tears♪

5
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:23,100
♪Through the storm♪

6
00:00:23,220 --> 00:00:27,180
♪I'd like to travel with you♪

7
00:00:28,940 --> 00:00:30,370
[Beauty Strategy Season 1]

8
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:34,980
[Adapted from The Spirit Queen
by TUTU on Kuaikan Comic]

9
00:00:34,980 --> 00:00:37,980
[Episode 12]
[Lingzhi's Heart]

10
00:00:39,420 --> 00:00:39,980
Your Majesty,

11
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,260
Her Majesty
has made the Dark Viper Toxin

12
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:44,100
and tested it on Snow King.

13
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:46,980
Looks like

14
00:00:48,060 --> 00:00:50,100
she'll soon start a war
against other clans.

15
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:52,220
Now, Snow King is in trouble.

16
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:53,660
Shall we save him

17
00:00:53,780 --> 00:00:55,020
and ally with his clan?

18
00:00:56,020 --> 00:00:56,580
No.

19
00:00:57,220 --> 00:00:58,220
Her Majesty can't wait to see me

20
00:00:58,220 --> 00:00:59,580
collude with other clans.

21
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:01,940
We can't save a little but lose a lot.

22
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:04,220
It will break our whole plan.

23
00:01:04,780 --> 00:01:05,460
Then...

24
00:01:06,660 --> 00:01:07,940
will you make Lady Ling your consort?

25
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:13,740
Is it true?

26
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:16,060
Lady Ling indeed asked to be a consort.

27
00:01:16,420 --> 00:01:18,340
But His Majesty didn't agree to it
on the spot.

28
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:21,740
I can't wait any longer.

29
00:01:22,260 --> 00:01:23,620
I must get rid of what's in my way

30
00:01:24,140 --> 00:01:26,420
and make His Majesty work for me.

31
00:01:27,540 --> 00:01:31,060
Or the Phantom clan will
end up like the Snow clan.

32
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:33,140
We've been watching

33
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:34,500
over that young slave Qingyan.

34
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,900
She sneaked into the prison to find
out some information for Lady Ling.

35
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:39,940
Once we get her testimony,

36
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:42,300
Lady Ling will be convicted.

37
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:43,660
Good.

38
00:01:44,260 --> 00:01:45,140
Take action when the day breaks.

39
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:46,140
Yes.

40
00:01:48,380 --> 00:01:49,020
Shana.

41
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:51,860
How long have you been serving me?

42
00:01:52,260 --> 00:01:52,940
For ten years.

43
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,220
If one day,

44
00:01:59,900 --> 00:02:01,340
I were captured,

45
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,660
I wouldn't be your burden.

46
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:05,740
I've been in charge of the harem
for so many years

47
00:02:06,340 --> 00:02:08,140
just to prevent this from happening.

48
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:11,420
You may leave now.

49
00:02:26,060 --> 00:02:26,860
Lingzhi.

50
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:35,500
This is the sweet soup
I asked the chefs to make.

51
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:36,460
Taste it.

52
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:50,620
Tastes great.

53
00:02:58,750 --> 00:02:59,920
[Tinghan Palace]

54
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,620
What do you want?

55
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:24,540
Lingzhi,

56
00:03:24,820 --> 00:03:26,860
why do you look unhappy?

57
00:03:32,020 --> 00:03:33,380
I've arranged everything

58
00:03:33,940 --> 00:03:35,260
for you so you can leave the palace.

59
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:38,500
Qingyan, leave now.

60
00:03:41,580 --> 00:03:42,460
Lingzhi,

61
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:44,900
please don't expel me.
I don't want to leave.

62
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:47,540
Consort Huan suspects

63
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:48,780
that Lady Ling is keeping a guilty maid.

64
00:03:49,220 --> 00:03:49,900
Get out of the way.

65
00:03:50,820 --> 00:03:52,580
You're here to capture a maid randomly
without any evidence.

66
00:03:52,780 --> 00:03:53,900
It's against the palace rules.

67
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:56,020
Now, I'll show you

68
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:57,620
what palace rules are.

69
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:08,660
Qingyan,

70
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,460
my life will be more and more dangerous.

71
00:04:12,860 --> 00:04:14,500
I won't put you in any danger.

72
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,660
Then keep me with you
for some more time.

73
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:19,100
I beg you.

74
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:23,580
When you're out of the palace,

75
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,660
you should have regular sleep

76
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:27,340
and meals.

77
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:31,260
But...

78
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:36,220
But I only want to stay...

79
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:37,780
with you.

80
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:19,860
Lingzhi, hand over that maid.

81
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:23,260
Unfortunately,

82
00:05:24,460 --> 00:05:26,180
you're late, Your Grace.

83
00:05:27,380 --> 00:05:28,940
She is no longer here.

84
00:05:57,180 --> 00:05:59,260
I hate to leave her.

85
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:01,660
But someone taught me

86
00:06:03,260 --> 00:06:04,740
that being soft-hearted in this palace

87
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:07,740
is a fatal weakness.

88
00:06:09,420 --> 00:06:09,940
Good.

89
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:14,420
That person has taught you so well

90
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:18,940
that makes me want
to kill you immediately.

91
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:20,900
You flatter me, Your Grace.

92
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:23,540
Lady Ling,

93
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:25,700
are you aware of your sin?

94
00:06:26,980 --> 00:06:28,420
Kneel now!

95
00:06:29,780 --> 00:06:31,820
I don't know what crime I've committed.

96
00:06:36,340 --> 00:06:37,460
According to the palace rules,

97
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:40,820
a maid can't leave the palace
before she's 30.

98
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:42,020
Your Grace,

99
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:44,980
His Majesty specially permitted
Qingyan to leave.

100
00:06:45,860 --> 00:06:48,660
There are hierarchies in the palace.

101
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,660
You should remember

102
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:53,140
that His Majesty is the Emperor

103
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:57,100
while you're only his consort.

104
00:06:58,540 --> 00:06:58,940
You...

105
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:00,460
Sorry, Your Grace.

106
00:07:01,260 --> 00:07:02,540
His Majesty asked to see me.

107
00:07:03,260 --> 00:07:04,700
I'll take my leave.

108
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:09,540
Lingzhi.

109
00:07:19,860 --> 00:07:23,060
You're not his first sword.

110
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:25,940
Over all these years,

111
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:30,340
I've broken all his swords.

112
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:36,500
You're no exception.

113
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,700
It's because, over all these years,

114
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:43,980
the two clans have been in peace.

115
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:49,380
But now Her Majesty
wants to start a war against your clan.

116
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:55,020
How much longer
can you still be in charge?

117
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:55,740
You...

118
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,940
You lied to Consort Huan
that I wanted to see you,

119
00:08:11,780 --> 00:08:13,620
deceived her, and provoked her openly.

120
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:18,460
All these are capital crimes.

121
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:23,180
I'm guilty.
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

122
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:36,820
How shall I punish you?

123
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:40,340
Make me your consort.

124
00:08:41,340 --> 00:08:42,820
That will be

125
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:45,460
the most severe punishment for me.

126
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:49,540
You have a glib tongue.

127
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,140
It doesn't make any sense.

128
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:53,780
If you make me your consort,

129
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,540
Consort Huan will
do her best to kill me.

130
00:08:56,940 --> 00:08:58,340
By then, she'll torture me

131
00:08:58,820 --> 00:09:00,500
ten times more cruelly.

132
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:03,580
I'll be stuck in purgatory.

133
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,660
I thought you wouldn't know this.

134
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:12,580
But when I'm your consort,

135
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:15,260
even if I have to live in purgatory,

136
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:17,780
I will help you get the real power,

137
00:09:18,500 --> 00:09:19,900
Your Majesty.

138
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:32,900
You're ambitious.

139
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:37,940
Go back now.

140
00:09:39,300 --> 00:09:41,260
Your Majesty, please think about it.

141
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:48,180
I'll draft the edict
to make you my consort.

142
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,660
Your presence will only distract me.

143
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:52,260
Thank you, Your Majesty.

144
00:09:58,100 --> 00:09:59,700
Your Grace, the horse is ready.

145
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:08,780
Send a message by pigeon
to our clansmen outside the city.

146
00:10:09,060 --> 00:10:10,460
Have them watch over every crossing

147
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:11,900
and allow no one to pass by.

148
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:12,540
Yes.

149
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,300
I guess Lady Ling has no idea

150
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:15,580
that before I married His Majesty,

151
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:17,060
I was a general of my clan.

152
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:20,020
And people really die
on the battlefield.

153
00:10:21,860 --> 00:10:23,140
I'll wait for the good news, Your Grace.

154
00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:28,020
Lady Ling...

155
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:29,900
Oh, no. Consort Ling.

156
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:31,700
His Majesty personally chose

157
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:33,500
this outfit for you

158
00:10:33,660 --> 00:10:35,020
for the ceremony
of making you a consort.

159
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:35,860
It looks great.

160
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:43,100
What are you doing here again?

161
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:45,900
Your Grace,

162
00:10:46,140 --> 00:10:48,500
this is Consort Huan's present
for your promotion.

163
00:10:48,940 --> 00:10:49,980
Please take it.

164
00:10:51,180 --> 00:10:52,460
Bring my gratitude to Her Grace.

165
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,700
Her Grace has a message for you.

166
00:11:11,500 --> 00:11:13,020
If you want Qingyan to live,

167
00:11:13,460 --> 00:11:15,180
you must abdicate.

168
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:29,220
♪My eyebrows are outlined
against the rain♪

169
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:32,960
♪Lovesickness tastes like bitter wine♪

170
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:36,660
♪The wind sighs softly at our destiny♪

171
00:11:37,060 --> 00:11:40,300
♪Love and hate are forever gone♪

172
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:44,100
♪Don't ask where I'm going♪

173
00:11:44,540 --> 00:11:47,740
♪I won't change my love for you♪

174
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:51,460
♪My destination is my fate,
my obsession is to wait♪

175
00:11:51,740 --> 00:11:55,540
♪I'm just destined to wander♪

176
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:59,220
♪If I can be greedy♪

177
00:11:59,580 --> 00:12:02,940
♪You will be what I want for this life♪

178
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,660
♪Yet you don't even look back
when the song ends♪

179
00:12:06,940 --> 00:12:10,420
♪Who gets stuck in the dream with me?♪

180
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:13,980
♪Old memories never yield♪

181
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:17,820
♪Under the spring breeze,
the flowers bloom as before♪

182
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:21,500
♪When clouds are dispersed,
I will disappear♪

183
00:12:21,780 --> 00:12:24,860
♪However far away I stay,
I'm always who I am♪

184
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:29,780
♪The moonlight gently falls
into your eyes♪
